long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Mass delete likes for your Twitter (x.com) account.

Each time you start to mass delete the likes, the app will delete likes for 12 minutes.

Twitter has rate limit of 900 per 15 minutes. In order to prevent violating this limit, the Chrome Extension terminates after 12 minutes.
